Node 4: Tool-Touched Spriggans
Description: The party reaches a clearing where the missing woodcutters had been working. Stumps of ancient trees dot the area, and abandoned woodcutting tools lie scattered about. But the trees have grown backΓÇöwrong. They've grown around and through the tools, creating twisted hybrid creatures.
The Setback: Three Tool-Touched Spriggans guard this clearing. These are corrupted nature spirits that have fused with the abandoned woodcutting equipment, creating grotesque hybrids of wood and steel. They see the party as more desecrators and attack without hesitation.
3x Tool-Touched Spriggan (Novice Tier TL 1)
One spriggan has a woodsman's axe fused to its arm, another has a saw blade, and the third has smaller tools embedded in its bark-like skin. They move with an unnatural, jerky gait.

